  <brief_title>Multi-center Clinical Trials of Sanjie Analgesic Capsule in Treating Endometriosis</brief_title>
  <official_title>A Randomized, Double-blind, Placebo-controlled Post-marketing Study to Assess the Treatment Effect of Sanjie Analgesic Capsule in Treating Endometriosis - Associated Pain</official_title>
